Nutella Strawberry Toast

5 min
$2.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

NutsGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Course:

Description

A deliciously sweet and creamy toast topped with fresh strawberries, perfect for breakfast or a snack!

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • nutella: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh strawberries: 4-5, sliced
  • honey (optional): 1 teaspoon
